{"tid":2180475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係一個好重要的日子","createTime":"2020-08-30T01:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T07:50:32.000Z","uid":301707,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d0c0beea09418605d9481dd9281561cea7e8d0","tid":2180475,"uid":301707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">今日係香港重光75週年。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n75年前嘅今日，英國皇家海軍少將夏愨（Sir Cecil Harcourt，夏慤道個個夏慤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）率領英國皇家海軍特遣艦隊抵港。艦隊下面嘅「海港部隊」負責喺8月30日進入藍塘海峽掃雷。之後，夏慤率領巡洋艦「迅敏號」（HMS Swiftsure）、一艘巡洋艦同埋三艘驅遂艦駛入香港。同一時間，《南華早報暨香港電訊報聯合刊》（South China Morning Post and The Hongkong Telegraph）亦都有印號外周街派。艦隊靠岸後，就派咗成堆日用品俾岸上面嘅市民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而當晚香港市區出現大規模慶祝活動，紀念打完仗同埋盟軍贏咗場仗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英軍登陸香港後釋放係拘留營嘅戰俘，並接收日軍戰俘。而係1943年成立嘅香港計劃組*，亦於9月抵港工作，進行重建工作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*香港計劃組負責籌備戰後管治香港嘅事務。1944年擔任香港計劃組組長嘅麥道高（David Mercer MacDougall）認為，英國政府應該比本地居民更平等的權利。除此之外，計劃小組建議喺香港設立市議會，並改革行政立法兩局，旨在以民主改革增加談判的籌碼，避免美國支持中華民國收返香港；又建議喺市區設立市議會，設有洋人和華人代表，其中華人代表係以選舉產生，藉此增加華人嘅歸屬感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n豉油：<br />\n【香港重光】夏慤道背後的意義<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wetoasthk.com/【香港重光】夏慤道背後的意義/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2F%E3%80%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E3%80%91%E5%A4%8F%E6%85%A4%E9%81%93%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLARUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=23c707b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wetoasthk.com/【香港重光】夏慤道背後的意義/</a><br />\n1945 年香港重光 &mdash; 中英爭奪香港，如何收科？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/1945-年香港重光-中英爭奪香港-如何收科/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F1945-%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E7%88%AD%E5%A5%AA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%94%B6%E7%A7%91%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLARUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=c74bd320\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F1945-%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%AD%E8%8B%B1%E7%88%AD%E5%A5%AA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%94%B6%E7%A7%91%2F&h=abaf231c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/1945-年香港重光-中英爭奪香港-如何收科/</a><br />\nLuard, Tim. Escape from Hong Kong : Admiral Chan Chak's Christmas day dash, 1941. Hong Kong University Press. 2012. 215-216<br />\n徐承恩. 城邦舊事: 十二本書看香港本土史 (修訂版). Red Publish. 2016: 145."},{"pid":"0b8f0f6bd5521560809a4939458e79dbafa7e1cc","tid":2180475,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8315c45668dd4e2f9e70b558c6322a9dde219b58","tid":2180475,"uid":301707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:23:42.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n【明夷待訪，等待重光】1944 年版香港重光郵票？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/明夷待訪-等待重光-1944-年版香港重光郵票/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%98%8E%E5%A4%B7%E5%BE%85%E8%A8%AA-%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89-1944-%E5%B9%B4%E7%89%88%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E9%83%B5%E7%A5%A8%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLARUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=fc607c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%98%8E%E5%A4%B7%E5%BE%85%E8%A8%AA-%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89-1944-%E5%B9%B4%E7%89%88%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E9%83%B5%E7%A5%A8%2F&