g&h=a214ca1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1945年9月16日，夏慤睇住日本副海軍上將藤田類太郎喺投降書上簽字（Source：Wikicommon）<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a2/1945_liberation_of_Hong_Kong_at_Cenotaph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Fa2%2F1945_liberation_of_Hong_Kong_at_Cenotaph.jpg&h=5f3025a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中華民國和同埋英國雙方喺1945年9月舉行勝利巡遊。（Source：Wikicommon）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2010dc11e0fd88a09bc8184cbb6b723158fdd660","tid":2180475,"uid":301707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:32:50.000Z","msg":"continue to push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae49ba9fb66d263e502ff7f5cd2a9337e872841d","tid":2180475,"uid":301707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6357f0a0970da8d9b8cd75bed2d48ba6e67193c8","tid":2180475,"uid":301707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:39:39.000Z","msg":"香港重光入邊亦都涉及到中華民國、英國同埋嘅政治角力。遲下可以講下。<br />\n另外英國接收返香港後，亦都喺食物供應、控制匯率、公共衛生、及法治等等做咗好多功夫，以加快重建速度，挽回英國聲譽之餘，亦重奪民心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e07683a7e1f5ad7587d5060659a17c17cca978","tid":2180475,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fec275987b3c0728c2aba20dffa0db38e62e9b7","tid":2180475,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T0